        </div>
        <div>
          <strong>98%</strong>
          <span>Customer satisfaction</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="section" id="categories">
      <div class="section-header">
        <p class="eyebrow">Popular categories</p>
        <h2>Everything your machine needs</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="category-grid">
        <article class="category-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1486262715619-67b85e0b08d3?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="Engine bay performance parts">
          <div>
            <h3>Engine Parts</h3>
            <p>Filters, belts, plugs, mounts, sensors, and rebuild essentials.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="category-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1619642751034-765dfdf7c58e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="Car brake system close-up">
          <div>
            <h3>Brake Systems</h3>
            <p>Pads, rotors, calipers, lines, and braking upgrades.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="category-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517524008697-84bbe3c3fd98?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="Modern car interior accessories">
          <div>
            <h3>Car Accessories</h3>
            <p>Interior, exterior, tech, detailing, and protection gear.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="category-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503376780353-7e6692767b70?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="Sports car lighting at night">
          <div>
            <h3>Lighting</h3>
            <p>LED headlights, fog lamps, indicators, and styling kits.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="category-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503736334956-4c8f8e92946d?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="Performance wheels on sports car">
          <div>
            <h3>Tires & Wheels</h3>
            <p>Alloys, tires, wheel care, spacers, caps, and lug hardware.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="category-card">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1492144534655-ae79c964c9d7?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="Performance sports car">
          <div>
            <h3>Performance Parts</h3>
            <p>Intakes, exhausts, suspension, tuning, and track upgrades.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="section why-section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <p class="eyebrow">Why choose us</p>
        <h2>Parts buying without second guessing</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-grid">
        <article class="feature-card">
          <span class="feature-icon">&#10003;</span>
          <h3>Genuine Parts</h3>
          <p>Carefully sourced items from verified suppliers and known brands.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="feature-card">
          <span class="feature-icon">$</span>
          <h3>Affordable Pricing</h3>
          <p>Competitive pricing across essential parts and premium upgrades.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="feature-card">
          <span class="feature-icon">&#8599;</span>
          <h3>Fast Matching</h3>
          <p>Get guidance on fitment before you confirm the final order.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="feature-card">
          <span class="feature-icon">&#9742;</span>
          <h3>Customer Support</h3>
          <p>Talk directly with a seller through WhatsApp for clear answers.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="section about-section" id="about">
      <div class="about-image">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1525609004556-c46c7d6cf023?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Premium automotive workshop with performance car">
      </div>
      <div class="about-copy">
        <p class="eyebrow">Brand story</p>
        <h2>Performance parts with real-world trust</h2>
        <p>EzyParts helps drivers, riders, garages, and enthusiasts source reliable vehicle parts without the friction. From everyday maintenance to sharper performance upgrades, every order is handled with a focus on compatibility, quality, and direct communication.</p>
        <p>Browse the range, message us through WhatsApp, and confirm the right fit before buying.</p>
        <a class="text-link" href="#contact">Speak with a parts specialist</a>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="section process-section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <p class="eyebrow">How it works</p>
        <h2>Simple ordering, confirmed by a real seller</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="process-grid">
        <article class="process-card">
          <span>01</span>
          <h3>Browse Parts</h3>
          <p>Explore categories and shortlist the part, accessory, or upgrade you need.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="process-card">
          <span>02</span>
          <h3>Message on WhatsApp</h3>
          <p>Send your vehicle details and talk with the seller to confirm fitment.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="process-card">
          <span>03</span>
          <h3>Confirm the Order</h3>
          <p>Finalize availability, payment, delivery, and pickup details with confidence.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="section testimonials-section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <p class="eyebrow">Customer reviews</p>
        <h2>Trusted by drivers and workshops</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonial-shell">
        <button class="carousel-btn" type="button" data-direction="prev" aria-label="Previous review">&#8249;</button>
        <div class="testimonial-track">
          <article class="testimonial-card is-active">
            <div class="stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
            <p>"Got the exact brake kit for my BMW within a day. The fitment check saved me from ordering the wrong part."</p>
            <h3>Ryan M.</h3>
          </article>
          <article class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
            <p>"Clean service, genuine accessories, and quick WhatsApp replies. Perfect for busy workshop orders."</p>
            <h3>Naveen Auto Care</h3>
          </article>
          <article class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
            <p>"The performance intake and lighting upgrade arrived well packed. Premium experience from start to finish."</p>
            <h3>Akila S.</h3>
          </article>
        </div>
        <button class="carousel-btn" type="button" data-direction="next" aria-label="Next review">&#8250;</button>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="cta-banner">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Limited promotion</p>
        <h2>Ready to sharpen your build?</h2>
        <p>Get seller-backed recommendations on accessories, maintenance parts, and performance upgrades.</p>
      </div>
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/shop">Get Best Price</a>
    </section>
    <section class="section newsletter-section" id="contact">
      <div class="contact-panel">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">Contact and newsletter</p>
          <h2>Talk parts, fitment, and offers</h2>
          <p>Send your request, vehicle model, and preferred part. We will help you confirm the right match before the order.</p>
          <a class="whatsapp-link" href="https://wa.me/94770000000" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Message on WhatsApp</a>
        </div>
        <form class="newsletter-form" id="newsletterForm">
          <label for="name">Name</label>
          <input id="name" name="name" type="text" placeholder="Your name" required>
          <label for="email">Email</label>
          <input id="email" name="email" type="email" placeholder="you@example.com" required>
          <label for="request">Part request</label>
          <textarea id="request" name="request" rows="4" placeholder="Tell us what you need"></textarea>
          <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Send Request</button>
          <p class="form-message" id="formMessage" role="status" aria-live="polite"></p>
        </form>
      </div>
      <div class="preorder-tab" onclick="togglePreorder()">
      <div class="preorder-tab">
        Pre-Orders
      </div>
      <div class="preorder-popup" id="preorderPopup">
        <button class="close-btn" onclick="togglePreorder()">✕</button>
        <button class="close-btn">✕</button>
        <h3>Pre-Orders</h3>
        <p>Contact us for pre-orders</p>
        <p>Need a part we don't have in stock? Message us for custom pre-orders.</p>
        <a class="whatsapp-link" href="https://wa.me/94771234567" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Message on WhatsApp</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
 

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
